# **MeetMate | SAAR – Self-aware Adaptive Agentic RAG**

**Self-Reflective / Corrective RAG Engine, Tool-Calling & Multi-Stage Meeting Assistant (Pre → In → Post)**

## **0\) Tóm tắt điều hành**

MeetMate triển khai một kiến trúc **stage-aware, multi-agent LangGraph** để chuẩn hóa vòng đời UC\&C của cuộc họp: **Pre-Meeting → In-Meeting → Post-Meeting**. Tất cả agent dùng **một typed MeetingState**, **luôn grounded trên enterprise RAG**, và phát sinh **tool-call có cấu trúc** (task/follow-up/docs) trong hạ tầng **bank-controlled, PII-safe, fully audited**.

**MeetMate SAAR architecture**

Điểm cốt lõi của SAAR:

* **Stage-aware LangGraph routing**: 1 StateGraph entry, điều kiện stage/sensitivity/SLA dẫn vào pre/in/post subgraph  
* **Shared MeetingState xuyên suốt**: Pre → In → Post reuse state để giữ nhất quán agenda/transcript/ADR/RAG hits, giảm re-query và dễ audit  
* **Adaptive RAG-first, permission-aware**: Unified RAG (pgvector \+ BM25 \+ ACL/metadata filter) trả về normalized DocumentSnippets vào state  
* **No-source → no-answer** cho nội dung regulated \+ citations bắt buộc  
* **Tool-calling là output hạng nhất**: schema-defined functions \+ executor backend xử lý UI approval, idempotency, và audit log theo meeting

---

## **1\) Mục tiêu, phạm vi và nguyên tắc kiến trúc AI**

### **1.1 Mục tiêu (AI Layer)**

1. Chuẩn hóa pipeline **Pre → In → Post** trên **một kiến trúc AI chung**.  
2. Tách bạch rõ:  
* **Business logic họp**: agenda, action, decision, risk, minutes, highlights…  
* **AI infrastructure**: VNPT SmartVoice (ASR), VNPT SmartBot (LLM/intent), RAG Service, tool-calling, guardrails…

3. Đảm bảo:  
* **In-Meeting realtime** (sub-second → vài giây cho recap/ADR/Q\&A tùy tick)  
* **Pre/Post** ưu tiên **độ chính xác \+ long-context**  
* **Bảo mật ngân hàng**: không rò PII/transcript raw ra ngoài policy tenant; đầy đủ audit & e-discovery  
* **Quan sát & kiểm soát chi phí**: token budget, SLA routing, caching, tracing theo meeting

### **1.2 SAAR \= “Self-aware \+ Self-reflective/Corrective” trong RAG**

SAAR không chỉ “Retrieve → Generate”, mà bổ sung **các vòng kiểm định và sửa sai**:

* **Grader/Judge** đánh giá chất lượng/độ phù hợp của retrieved context.  
* **Self-Reflect / Checker** phát hiện thiếu sót/mâu thuẫn/hallucination risk, sau đó **rewrite query / retrieve lại / tăng top-k có kiểm soát** trước khi chốt đáp án.

---

## **2\) Kiến trúc tổng quan (End-to-End)**

### **2.1 Các khối hệ thống chính**

1. **Client Layer (Desktop/Meetings add-in or SDK)**  
* Stream audio (GoogleMeet/VNPTGoMeet)  
* Gửi event: `transcript`, `question (Ask-AI)`, `confirm_tool`  
* Nhận: `recap`, `adr_update`, `qa_answer`, `tool_suggestion`, `error`

2. **ASR – VNPT SmartVoice**  
* Trả transcript chunk có diarization \+ timestamp; phân biệt `is_final=false/true`.  
* (Tuỳ chọn) micro-summary theo chu kỳ 30–60s để giảm noise cho intent/topic.

3. **Backend – FastAPI \+ WebSocket \+ LangGraph**  
* Trung tâm routing, RAG, LLM calls, tool suggestion/execution và audit.  
   MeetMate SAAR architecture

4. **Unified RAG Service (pgvector/Milvus \+ BM25)**  
* Hybrid retrieval \+ metadata filters \+ ACL  
* Trả normalized snippets (doc\_id, chunk\_id, offsets, effective\_date, permission\_scope…)

5. **Tool Executor & Integration Layer**  
* Enforce allow-list theo stage/sensitivity  
* Human-in-the-loop (In-Meeting 1-click confirm)  
* Idempotency \+ audit trail

6. **Observability & Governance**  
* Tracing end-to-end theo `meeting_id` & `user_id/intent`  
* Log LLM/RAG/tool calls; checkpoint state (LangGraph) phục vụ replay/forensics.

## **3\) LangGraph chuẩn hóa: Router \+ Subgraphs \+ Shared State**

## ![][image1]

### **3.1 “Single entry graph” và điều phối theo stage**

* Một StateGraph entry; stage/sensitivity/SLA/tenant\_policy điều khiển conditional edges vào 3 subgraph: **Pre / In / Post**.  
   MeetMate SAAR architecture  
* Mỗi subgraph có **runtime profile riêng**: model endpoint, context window, token budget, tool allow-list.  
   MeetMate SAAR architecture

### **3.2 Typed Shared State (MeetingState)**

Tất cả agent dùng **một typed MeetingState**, đảm bảo nhất quán xuyên suốt.

**Đề xuất schema (rút gọn, đủ triển khai):**

`MeetingState:`  
  `meeting_id: string`  
  `tenant_id: string`  
  `stage: PRE_MEETING | IN_MEETING | POST_MEETING`  
  `sensitivity: LOW | MEDIUM | HIGH`  
  `sla_profile: REALTIME | NEAR_REALTIME | BATCH`  
  `tenant_policy:`  
    `llm_provider: VNPT_SMARTBOT | AZURE_OAI | ONPREM`  
    `region: string`  
    `external_call_allowed: bool`  
    `retention_mode: ZERO_RETENTION | BANK_LOGGING`  
  `participants:`  
    `organizer: { user_id, display_name, role }`  
    `attendees: [ { user_id, display_name, role } ]`  
  `permissions:`  
    `rag_acl_scope: { departments, projects, doc_types }`  
    `tool_acl_scope: { allowed_tools, require_confirm_tools }`  
  `calendar_context:`  
    `title: string`  
    `description: string`  
    `start_time: datetime`  
    `end_time: datetime`  
    `recurring_series_id: string?`  
    `attached_docs: [ { doc_id, source, permission } ]`  
    `entities: { project_id?, unit_id?, topic_tags? }`  
  `transcript:`  
    `buffer_partial: [TranscriptChunk]`  
    `full_final: [TranscriptChunk]`  
    `window: [TranscriptChunk]   # rolling window for realtime`  
    `topics: [TopicSegment]`  
    `current_topic_id: string?`  
  `rag:`  
    `last_query: string?`  
    `rag_docs: [DocumentSnippet]`  
    `citations: [Citation]       # doc/timecode citations`  
  `adr:`  
    `actions: [ActionItem]`  
    `decisions: [DecisionItem]`  
    `risks: [RiskItem]`  
    `history: [AdrEvent]         # incremental updates`  
  `qa:`  
    `last_question: string?`  
    `last_answer: string?`  
    `qa_history: [QaTurn]`  
  `tools:`  
    `suggestions: [ToolSuggestion]`  
    `executions: [ToolExecution]`  
  `metrics:`  
    `llm_calls: int`  
    `rag_calls: int`  
    `token_used: int`  
    `latency_ms: { asr, rag, llm, end_to_end }`  
    `cost_estimate: { llm, embedding, storage }`  
  `debug:`  
    `routing: { chosen_subgraph, model_profile, tool_profile }`  
    `graders: { relevance_score, faithfulness_score, conflict_flags }`

## **4\) Stage-Aware AI Router (3 giai đoạn)**

### **4.1 Input & Policy**

Router nhận:

* `stage`: PRE / IN / POST  
* `sensitivity`: LOW / MEDIUM / HIGH  
* `sla_profile`: REALTIME / NEAR\_REALTIME / BATCH  
* `tenant_policy`: provider/region/retention/tools…

Router quyết định:

1. **Subgraph**: Pre / In / Post  
2. **Model profile**: `fast` (streaming/low latency) vs `strong` (quality/long-context)  
3. **SLO/FinOps config**: context window \+ budget/quota  
4. **Guardrails & compliance**: redaction need, allow-list tool, audit mode

### **4.2 Bảng mapping (chuẩn hóa)**

**PRE\_MEETING**

* SLA: NEAR\_REALTIME/BATCH  
* Model: strong (8K+ context)  
* Tools: `rag_search`, `fetch_calendar`, `send_pre_read`, `open_doc`, `collect_questions`  
* Guardrails: ACL strict, citations bắt buộc.

**IN\_MEETING**

* SLA: REALTIME/NEAR\_REALTIME  
* Model: fast streaming; context nhỏ (rolling window)  
* Tools: `create_task`, `schedule_meeting`, `attach_doc`, `poll_vote` (đều require confirm)  
* Tick scheduler giới hạn LLM calls theo interval \+ token budget

**POST\_MEETING**

* SLA: BATCH  
* Model: strong long-context; map-reduce nếu transcript dài  
* Tools: `generate_minutes`, `sync_task`, `render_highlights`, `archive_compliance`  
* Compliance: WORM \+ retention \+ e-discovery.

---

## **5\) SAAR Core Engine: Self-Reflective / Corrective RAG (chuẩn hóa cho mọi stage)**

### **5.1 Mục tiêu**

* Luôn **RAG-first**; prompt chỉ xây trên retrieved context; **no source → no answer**.  
   MeetMate SAAR architecture  
* Tăng độ đúng bằng **vòng kiểm định** (grader/judge/checker) trước khi trả lời / trước khi tạo tool suggestion.

### **5.2 Pipeline chuẩn (khuyến nghị dùng chung)**

**A. Query Understanding & Scope**

* Entity extraction: project\_id/unit\_id/topic\_id  
* Determine scope: meeting-only vs project docs vs global policies  
* Apply ACL/effective\_date filters.

**B. Retrieve (Hybrid)**

* Vector search \+ BM25  
* top\_k nhỏ theo SLA; có thể “escalate” nếu grader fail.

**C. Grade & Judge**

* **Grader Agent**: chấm relevance, freshness, permission fit, policy fit  
* **Judge Agent**: quyết định “context đủ chưa?”; nếu chưa: rewrite query \+ retrieve lại (controlled retries)

**D. Generate (VNPT SmarBot LLM)**

* Strictly grounded answer \+ citations.

**E. Self-Reflect / Correct**

* Checker so sánh output với context: thiếu quyết định/thiếu action? mâu thuẫn?  
* Nếu fail: corrective loop (retrieve bổ sung hoặc yêu cầu “không có dữ liệu phù hợp”).

### **5.3 Quy tắc dừng (Stop Conditions)**

* Max retries (vd 2 lần)  
* Token budget per stage  
* Nếu vẫn thiếu nguồn: trả “không có dữ liệu phù hợp trong phạm vi được phép”

---

## **6\) Pre-Meeting Subgraph (Agenda \+ Pre-Read \+ History-aware RAG)**

### **6.1 Runtime flow chuẩn**

1. **Calendar & Meeting Context Ingest** (Graph/LOffice)  
* Sync meeting, detect topic/type/unit/recurring pattern

2. **History & RAG Retrieval (History-aware)**  
* Ưu tiên: minutes cùng series/project, pending actions/unresolved decisions/open risks, attachments, templates, cùng project\_id/topic\_id, recency by effective\_date.

3. **Agenda & Pre-Read Generation (Strong profile)**  
* Agenda 3–7 items \+ time allocation \+ presenters; Pre-Read pack: link \+ short summary \+ citations

4. **Pre-Meeting Input Collection**

* Thu câu hỏi/risks/requests trước họp → lưu state để reuse In/Post

5. **Distribution & Pre-Meeting Q\&A**  
* Gửi Teams/email; hỗ trợ Q\&A scoped by meeting\_id

### **6.2 Pre-Meeting RAG Priority (chuẩn hóa scoring)**

Tầng ưu tiên và logic scoring có thể chuẩn hóa như:

* P0: Meeting history (series/project) \+ pending ADR boost  
* P1: Attachments \+ organizer pre-read templates  
* P2: Project/topic documents (effective\_date gần)  
* P3: Global policies/procedures (department \+ org-wide)  
   MeetMate SAAR architecture

SLA & chất lượng:

* Near-realtime agenda/Q\&A (\~3–5s), hỗ trợ long-context (\~8K tokens).  
   MeetMate SAAR architecture  
* Bắt buộc citations \+ no-source-no-answer.  
   MeetMate SAAR architecture  
* ACL-aware \+ PII redaction \+ masked logs.  
   MeetMate SAAR architecture

---

## **7\) In-Meeting Realtime Subgraph (Streaming Recap \+ ADR \+ Q\&A \+ Tool)**

### **7.1 Runtime architecture (chuẩn hóa theo 3 lớp routing)**

Backend là trung tâm routing/RAG/LLM/tool-calling/audit.

**(1) Stage Router**: chọn in\_meeting\_graph.  
**(2) Event Router \+ Tick Scheduler**: map message type → intent; kiểm soát tần suất LLM calls theo interval \+ token budget/window.  
**(3) Semantic Router**: SmartBot intent phân loại speech normal/question/command/decision/risk…

Toàn bộ request được route vào **Normal / Q\&A / Command-ADR flows**, nhưng **flow nào cũng kết thúc bằng Recap \+ ADR update** để state nhất quán

### **7.2 Luồng event (WS)**

* `transcript` (final) → update transcript\_window/full\_final  
* `question` → ưu tiên Q\&A, có thể “force tick”  
* `confirm_tool` → không gọi LLM; executor gọi API theo suggestion đã log

### **7.3 In-Meeting RAG (LightRAG-style, 3 tầng ưu tiên)**

* Meeting context (recent transcript, ADR, recap, attached docs)  
* Project/topic docs  
* Global bank-wide knowledge  
   → Retrieved snippets được re-rank và feed cho LLM cho Q\&A & recap/ADR enrichment, luôn citations.

Đảm bảo latency/cost:

* Small transcript window \+ RAG top-k nhỏ \+ tick scheduler để phản hồi trong vài giây và cap token usage.

Security/compliance:

* Data nằm trong bank/partner infra; PII redaction \+ zero-retention/no-logging nếu gọi external.

### **7.4 ADR & Tool-calling chuẩn hóa**

* ADR extractor tạo JSON có cấu trúc (Action/Decision/Risk)  
* ToolSuggestion node tạo payload \+ idempotency key; UI 1-click confirm; executor thực thi \+ audit.

---

## **8\) Post-Meeting Batch Subgraph (Minutes \+ Highlights \+ Compliance)**

### **8.1 Runtime flow**

1. **Transcript & ADR Ingest**: consolidate full transcript, topic segments, live recap timeline, ADR JSON, Q\&A logs, diarization.  
    MeetMate SAAR architecture  
2. **ADR Refinement**: dedupe/normalize, fill missing owners/deadlines, resolve conflicts, attach timecoded citations.  
    MeetMate SAAR architecture  
3. **Long-Context RAG Enrichment**: enrich Decisions/Risks bằng policy \+ historical minutes \+ related docs; reuse docs đã cited trong In-Meeting khi có thể.  
    MeetMate SAAR architecture  
4. **Minutes & Highlights Generation**: strong long-context; generate executive summary \+ full minutes \+ optional highlights.  
    MeetMate SAAR architecture  
5. **Render/Sync/Distribution**: export PDF/DOCX, sync actions sang Planner/Jira/LOffice, gửi Teams/email.  
    MeetMate SAAR architecture  
6. **Archive & Compliance**: WORM storage \+ audit trail \+ retention \+ e-discovery.  
    MeetMate SAAR architecture

### **8.2 Post-Meeting RAG Priority (Long-context consolidation)**

* Priority 1 (weight 1.0): transcript segments \+ topic summaries \+ refined ADR with timecodes  
* Priority 2 (weight 0.9): policy & compliance docs; ưu tiên doc đã referenced ở In-Meeting  
* Priority 3 (weight 0.7): historical context trong cùng project/series  
* Strategy: similarity × priority weight \+ recency \+ ADR/topic overlap; single-pass hoặc map-reduce cho transcript dài.

---

## **9\) Tool-Calling & Integration Layer (chuẩn enterprise, governed)**

### **9.1 Bộ function chuẩn (gợi ý chuẩn hóa signature)**

* `create_task(owner, content, due_date, source_meeting, source_timecode, idempotency_key)`  
* `schedule_meeting(datetime, participants, topic, source_meeting, idempotency_key)`  
* `fetch_policy(query|policy_id, scope, effective_date)`  
* `attach_doc(meeting_id, doc_id, reason)`  
* `send_summary(meeting_id, channel, recipients, format)`

### **9.2 Nguyên tắc vận hành**

* **Human-in-the-loop**: In-Meeting mọi tool quan trọng đều require confirm.  
* **Idempotency**: request-id per meeting/action để chống trùng.  
* **Validation backend**: schema validation \+ permission check \+ rate limit \+ circuit breaker.  
* **Audit**: log tool intent \+ tool execution \+ ai confirm \+ timestamp.

Tool-calling là output hạng nhất và executor chịu trách nhiệm UI approval \+ enterprise API calls \+ audit logs theo meeting.

---

## **10\) Guardrails, Governance, Observability & FinOps**

### **10.1 Guardrails**

* PII masking/tokenization trước khi gọi external provider (nếu policy cho phép).  
* Tool allow-list theo stage/sensitivity \+ role-based.  
* “No-source-no-answer” cho regulated responses.  
   MeetMate SAAR architecture

### **10.2 Observability**

* End-to-end logs keyed theo meeting & user/intent, trace mọi LLM call, RAG query, tool execution.  
* LangGraph checkpointing để replay/debug/incident review.

### **10.3 Cost & Performance**

* Router phân bổ workload: In-Meeting fast profile \+ context nhỏ; Post-Meeting strong profile \+ batch/map-reduce.  
* Token budget per meeting; caching FAQ/glossary; hạn chế spam Ask-AI.
